title: Step2 2-in-1 Ford® F-150 SVT Raptor
description: The Step2 2-in-1 Ford® F-150 SVT Raptor will be the coolest truck on the sidewalk! This red ride-on truck transforms from a push buggy to a kid powered riding toy. It features a front grille with working lights, tough rugged wheels with 360 degree turning, two working doors with latches, and a removable push handle and floor board.

transcripts: The two and one ford f-150 SVT raptor is one sweet ride, mom will love the grow with me feature the removable floorboard and push handle lets even the littlest kids enjoy riding around raptor style. The rugged wheels off 360 degree turning and like a real truck the bed has storage for rocks sticks and treasures. Be prepared to move out of the way of your little one honks the horn made in the USA with some important parts this miniature ford raptor is made of strong durable materials that will last for years of play.
